"title": "8120: following Jesus Christ",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8120: following jesus christ",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The NT provides examples of individuals who followed Jesus Christ and of the implications of this decision for their lives.</p>\n<h2>Examples of those who followed Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Crowds of people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:25\">MAT 4:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:1\">MAT 8:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:15\">MAT 12:15</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:7\">MRK 3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:13\">MAT 14:13</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:11\">LUK 9:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:2\">JHN 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:2\">MAT 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:15\">MRK 2:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:24\">MRK 5:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:11\">LUK 7:11</a></p>\n<h3>Those who were healed</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:34\">MAT 20:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:52\">MRK 10:52</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:43\">LUK 18:43</a></p>\n<h3>Those who were needy</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:27\">MAT 9:27</a></p>\n<h3>The disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:23\">MAT 8:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:51\">MRK 14:51</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:41\">MRK 15:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:15\">JHN 18:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who obeyed Jesus Christ's call to follow him</h2>\n<h3>Peter and Andrew</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:20\">MAT 4:18–4:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:18\">MRK 1:16–1:18</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:11\">LUK 5:11</a></p>\n<h3>James and John</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19-Mark1:20\">MRK 1:19–1:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Matthew</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:9\">MAT 9:9</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:14\">MRK 2:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:27-Luke5:28\">LUK 5:27–5:28</a></p>\n<h3>Philip</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:43-John1:45\">JHN 1:43–1:45</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who hesitated when called to follow Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:21\">MAT 19:21</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:21\">MRK 10:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:22-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:22–18:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:59-Luke9:60\">LUK 9:59–9:60</a></p>\n<h2>Wrong motives in following Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:11-1Cor1:13\">1CO 1:11–1:13</a></p>\n<h2>The cost of following Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Carrying one's cross</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24-Matt16:26\">MAT 16:24–16:26</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34-Mark8:37\">MRK 8:34–8:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23-Luke9:25\">LUK 9:23–9:25</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:37-Matt10:39\">MAT 10:37–10:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke14:25-Luke14:33\">LUK 14:25–14:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:23-John12:25\">JHN 12:23–12:25</a></p>\n<h3>Leaving security behind</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:19-Matt8:20\">MAT 8:19–8:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:57-Luke9:58\">LUK 9:57–9:58</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:61-Luke9:62\">LUK 9:61–9:62</a></p>\n<h3>Those who failed to persevere in following Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:66\">JHN 6:66</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Those who persevered under suffering in following Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:12-John13:17\">JHN 13:12–13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:19\">JHN 21:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:4\">ACT 22:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts24:14\">ACT 24:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:5\">ROM 15:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:1\">1CO 11:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:6\">1TH 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:20-1Pet2:23\">1PE 2:20–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:4\">REV 14:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:14\">REV 17:14</a></p>\n<h2>The blessings of following Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:27-Matt19:30\">MAT 19:27–19:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:28-Mark10:31\">MRK 10:28–10:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:28-Luke18:30\">LUK 18:28–18:30</a> <em>The reward is not on the basis of merit but the free gift promised to those who follow Jesus Christ.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:12\">JHN 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:26\">JHN 12:26</a></p>\n<h2>The limits on following Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:36\">JHN 13:36</a></p>",
